title: 2020 Week 6 Preview Show
itunes:title: 2020 Week 6 Preview Show
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Marc Sessler and Colleen Wolfe preview each upcoming game draft style, kicking off with Colleen's first overall pick Packers-Tampa Bay (3:20). Dan gets lucky with the second pick grabbing the Chiefs at Bills (9:30) and Marc surprises us with a pick we didn't see coming (19:01). Ricky makes a hard choice with her lock (1:01:00) and Colleen isn't happy with the NFC East (1:07:11)
